  "description": "A comforting, citrusy, and flavorful Portuguese-inspired dish perfect for a sick day, made with chicken breasts, shio-cure, and a hint of cinnamon. This easy-to-make recipe requires minimal effort and delivers a delicious, sugar-free-friendly meal.",
