  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Rinse the chicken breasts and pat them dry with paper towels.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together shio-cure, lemon juice, orange juice, olive oil, garlic powder, and cinnamon.",
    "Place the chicken breasts in a baking dish and brush the mixture evenly over both breasts.",
    "Sprinkle salt over both breasts.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes or until the chicken is cooked through and internal temperature reaches 165°F (74°C).",
    "Remove from the oven and sprinkle with chopped fresh parsley.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy!"
